{"tid":1459983,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"可唔可以對機場受阻既旅客講聲唔好意思？","createTime":"2019-08-13T00:21:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T11:51:03.000Z","uid":259542,"like":29,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"d58db257676b4699991d557b4bae2435ec4e2d16","tid":1459983,"uid":259542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T00:21:12.000Z","msg":"琴日發夢去左機場<br />\n見到真係好多人好迫<br />\n我個人覺得欣慰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係見到有d旅客望落去有d煩躁同疑惑<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">可唔可以同佢地講聲「唔好意思阻到佢地」<br />\n同埋講埋我地咁做既原因</span><br />\n我覺得拿到佢地既理解其實係好重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n靜一兩分鐘<br />\n比d講英文/國語（？）既人同在場旅客溝通一下就okay<br />\n無論係用<span style=\"color: red;\">大聲公講</span>或者<span style=\"color: red;\">一個個講</span>都可以<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">大聲公應該要拿到在場市民認可你既代表性先</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同受阻旅客做個briefing,輸出現況資訊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />對象應該集中係香港政府同犬隻,集中輸出民意"},{"pid":"c67952fc727ee41912ee08a979cd484a414b05e9","tid":1459983,"uid":98431,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T00:43:50.000Z","msg":"唔識英文就用英文文宣材料<br />\n<br />\nair drop"},{"pid":"f06888c09f7e2c7bb0fa71087c59a7b1ac519b0a","tid":1459983,"uid":168214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T00:51:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a17067660dd946b128ee4f293078632ea4047315","tid":1459983,"uid":41205,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T00:52:13.000Z","msg":"應該會仲燥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />sor咩ry姐，佢地要返班機咋"},{"pid":"ae2e1908117f7c4f86d91d7bd8394ce96aeb534e","tid":1459983,"uid":282654,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T00:52:55.000Z","msg":"冇咁既需要"},{"pid":"b8e9039366289a478a92f1084aa4fb6c4f6b9998","tid":1459983,"uid":64193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T00:53:03.000Z","msg":"夜晚既話<br />\n仲要分享小小 水同食物比佢地<br />\n鋪頭關哂既話真係無野食嫁<br />\n<br />\n顧己及人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3312969c2f0e9f3eef5f25ac748ff1534d0f3a21","tid":1459983,"uid":159876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T00:53:48.000Z","msg":"重點語句：我地已經走投無路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />比警方用催淚煙由住所，街道，商場，甚至係地鐵站迫到黎機場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e50350a7ccd45b5e309ff1005d706079ab320dea","tid":1459983,"uid":282115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T00:53:59.000Z","msg":"靜靜地<br />\n同每個行過既人細細聲講"},{"pid":"2e3b0934f921ca4c4be6472aeed8a241ab90bd0a","tid":1459983,"uid":159876,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a17067660dd946b128ee4f293078632ea4047315","tid":1459983,"uid":41205,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T00:52:13.000Z","msg":"應該會仲燥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />sor咩ry姐，佢地要返班機咋"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T00:54:01.000Z","msg":"利用同情心"},{"pid":"f9f9e8e88ffea6166bf098cb598a0006c86257e1","tid":1459983,"uid":3172,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"a17067660dd946b128ee4f293078632ea4047315","tid":1459983,"uid":41205,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T00:52:13.000Z","msg":"應該會仲燥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />sor咩ry姐，佢地要返班機咋"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T00:54:04.000Z","msg":"係   我覺得應該射返個波比政府  正如佢地乜都賴鳩示威者"},{"pid":"73aa8189088b05a0f06e88474d4adcaa76b9afe7","tid":1459983,"uid":159876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T00:55:26.000Z","msg":"機場集會可以正命為各區走難集中營<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"558f90b2bb412985ee62850244770e204b7c1088","tid":1459983,"uid":41205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f9f9e8e88ffea